dct_title_s: A topographical map of the southwestern Highlands : with the southwest portion of the Kittatinny Valley
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. In upper margin: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas sheet No. 2 (Southwestern Highlands). "From original surveys and levelings, based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey." Originally issued folded in covers 24 x 17 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton, N.J.] : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1885 ([New York] : Julius Bien & Co., Lith.)
